{"id":135,"ayahs":[{"number":60,"arabic":"وَهُوَ ٱلَّذِى يَتَوَفَّىٰكُم بِٱلَّيْلِ وَيَعْلَمُ مَا جَرَحْتُم بِٱلنَّهَارِ ثُمَّ يَبْعَثُكُمْ فِيهِ لِيُقْضَىٰٓ أَجَلٌۭ مُّسَمًّۭى ۖ ثُمَّ إِلَيْهِ مَرْجِعُكُمْ ثُمَّ يُنَبِّئُكُم بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"And He it is who causes you to be [like] dead at night, and knows what you work in daytime; and He brings you back to life each days in order that a term set [by Him] be fulfilled. In the end, unto Him you must return: and then He will make you understand all that you were doing [in life].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/849.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":54695,"position":1,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই  (আল্লাহ)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54696,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54697,"position":3,"arabic":"يَتَوَفَّىٰكُم","translation":"মৃত্যু(অর্থাৎ নিদ্রা)দেন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54698,"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلَّيْلِ","translation":"বেলায় রাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54699,"position":5,"arabic":"وَيَعْلَمُ","translation":"ও তিনি জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54700,"position":6,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54701,"position":7,"arabic":"جَرَحْتُم","translation":"অর্জন করো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54702,"position":8,"arabic":"بِٱلنَّهَارِ","translation":"বেলায় দিনের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54703,"position":9,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54704,"position":10,"arabic":"يَبْعَثُكُمْ","translation":"জাগান তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_060_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":54705,"position":11,"ar