Our messengers cause him to die: and they do not overlook [anyone].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/850.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":55289,"position":1,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55290,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْقَاهِرُ","translation":"পরাক্রমশালী","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55291,"position":3,"arabic":"فَوْقَ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55292,"position":4,"arabic":"عِبَادِهِۦ ۖ","translation":"দাসদের তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55294,"position":5,"arabic":"وَيُرْسِلُ","translation":"এবং পাঠান","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55295,"position":6,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"প্রতি তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55296,"position":7,"arabic":"حَفَظَةً","translation":"তত্ত্বাবধায়ক","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55297,"position":8,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ","translation":"এমনকি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55298,"position":9,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55299,"position":10,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"আসে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55300,"position":11,"arabic":"أَحَدَكُمُ","translation":"কারও তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55301,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتُ","translation":"মৃত্যু","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55302,"position":13,"arabic":"تَوَفَّتْهُ","translation":"মৃত্যু ঘটায় তার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55303,"position":14,"arabic":"رُسُلُنَا","translation":"আমাদের প্রেরিত (ফেরেশতাগণ)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55304,"position":15,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","translation":"এমতাবস্হায় যে তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55305,"position":16,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55306,"position":17,"arabic":"يُفَرِّطُونَ","translation":"ভুল করে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_061_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55307,"position":18,"arabic":"٦١","translation":"(৬১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":62,"arabic":"ثُمَّ رُدُّوٓا۟ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ مَوْلَىٰهُمُ ٱلْحَقِّ ۚ أَلَا لَهُ ٱلْحُكْمُ وَهُوَ أَسْرَعُ ٱلْحَٰسِبِينَ","translation":"And they [who have died] are thereupon brought before God, their true Lord Supreme. Oh, verily, His alone is all judgment: and He is the swiftest of all reckoners!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/851.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":55809,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55810,"position":2,"arabic":"رُدُّوٓا۟","translation":"তাদেরকে আনা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55811,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَى","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55812,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55813,"position":5,"arabic":"مَوْلَىٰهُمُ","translation":"(যিনি) তাদের মালিক","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55814,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْحَقِّ ۚ","translation":"প্রকৃত","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55816,"position":7,"arabic":"أَلَا","translation":"সাবধান","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55817,"position":8,"arabic":"لَهُ","translation":"জন্যে তাঁরই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55818,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْحُكْمُ","translation":"নির্দেশ দেয়ার ক্ষমতা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55819,"position":10,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55820,"position":11,"arabic":"أَسْرَعُ","translation":"দ্রুততর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55821,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْحَـٰسِبِينَ","translation":"হিসাব গ্রহণকারীদের (মধ্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_062_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55822,"position":13,"arabic":"٦٢","translation":"(৬২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":63,"arabic":"قُلْ مَن يُنَجِّيكُم مِّن ظُلُمَٰتِ ٱلْبَرِّ وَٱلْبَحْرِ تَدْعُونَهُۥ تَضَرُّعًۭا وَخُفْيَةًۭ لَّئِنْ أَنجَىٰنَا مِنْ هَٰذِهِۦ لَنَكُونَنَّ مِنَ ٱلشَّٰكِرِينَ","translation":"Say: \"Who is it that saves you from the dark dangers of land and sea [when] you call unto Him humbly, and in the secrecy of your hearts, `If He will but save us from this [distress], we shall most certainly be among the grateful'?\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/852.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":56364,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"(হে নাবী) বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_063_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56365,"position":2,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"\"কে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_063_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56366,"position":3,"arabic":"يُنَجِّيكُم","translation":"উদ্ধার করেন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_063_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56367,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_063_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56368,"position":5,"arabic":"ظُلُمَـٰتِ","translation":"অন্ধকারসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/006_063_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56369,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْبَرِّ","translation":"স্হলভাগের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_063_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56370,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱلْبَحْرِ","translation":"ও জলভাগের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_063_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56371,"position":8,"arabic":"تَدْعُونَهُۥ","translation":"(যখন) তোমরা ডাকো